<dl id="n12140b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12140b">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12140b"> 140(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> mother / father right</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">In all parts of the world another curious fact is to be observed, that the adoption of a new mode of life involved the transition from mother-right to father-right. <small> William James Perry, <a name="ORMR" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ORMR"><cite title="source">Origin of Magic and Religion</cite></a> (1923) 115</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
